Other symptoms may include fatigue, muscle pain, diarrhoea, stomach pain, loss of taste and abdominal pain.
The duration between exposure and symptoms is usually about five days, but it can be oscillating between two to fourteen days.
While most cases of moderate symptoms occur, some develop into viral pneumonia and multiple organs failure.
